    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Long PDF Summarizer\\n\",\"**NLP Project 43 of 100** — Summarize long PDFs with chapter-wise and global summaries using chunking + LLMs.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import subprocess, sys, importlib\\nfor pkg in ['numpy','pandas','transformers','torch']:\\n    try: importlib.import_module(pkg)\\n    except ImportError: subprocess.check_call([sys.executable,'-m','pip','install','-q',pkg])\\nprint('Ready.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import numpy as np, re\\nfrom transformers import pipeline\\nimport torch\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\ndevice = 0 if torch.cuda.is_available() else -1\\nprint(f'Device: {\\\"GPU\\\" if device==0 else \\\"CPU\\\"}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"# Simulate a long document with chapters\\nLONG_DOC = \\\"\\\"\\\"Chapter 1: Introduction to Machine Learning\\nMachine learning is a subset of artificial intelligence that focuses on building systems that learn from data. Unlike traditional programming where rules are explicitly coded, ML systems discover patterns automatically. The field has grown exponentially since 2012 when deep learning achieved breakthrough results in image recognition. Today, ML powers recommendations, search engines, autonomous vehicles, and medical diagnosis.\\n\\nChapter 2: Supervised Learning\\nSupervised learning uses labeled training data to learn a mapping from inputs to outputs. Classification predicts discrete categories while regression predicts continuous values. Common algorithms include logistic regression, decision trees, random forests, and gradient boosting. Neural networks have become dominant for complex tasks like image and text processing.\\n\\nChapter 3: Unsupervised Learning\\nUnsupervised learning finds patterns in unlabeled data. Clustering groups similar items together using algorithms like K-means, DBSCAN, and hierarchical clustering. Dimensionality reduction techniques like PCA and t-SNE help visualize high-dimensional data. These methods are crucial for exploratory data analysis and feature engineering.\\n\\nChapter 4: Deep Learning\\nDeep learning uses multi-layered neural networks to learn hierarchical representations. Convolutional neural networks excel at image tasks while recurrent networks handle sequential data. Transformers have revolutionized NLP with models like BERT and GPT. Training deep models requires large datasets and significant compute resources.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\nprint(f'Document length: {len(LONG_DOC)} characters')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Chunk-Based Summarization\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"summarizer = pipeline('summarization', model='facebook/bart-large-cnn', device=device)\\n\\ndef chunk_summarize(text, chunk_size=500):\\n    # Split by chapters\\n    chapters = re.split(r'Chapter \\\\d+:', text)\\n    chapters = [c.strip() for c in chapters if c.strip()]\\n    \\n    summaries = []\\n    for i, chapter in enumerate(chapters):\\n        try:\\n            summary = summarizer(chapter[:1024], max_length=80, min_length=20, do_sample=False)\\n            summaries.append(f'Chapter {i+1}: {summary[0][\\\"summary_text\\\"]}')\\n        except Exception as e:\\n            summaries.append(f'Chapter {i+1}: (Error: {e})')\\n    \\n    # Global summary\\n    combined = ' '.join(summaries)\\n    try:\\n        global_summary = summarizer(combined[:1024], max_length=100, min_length=30, do_sample=False)\\n        summaries.append(f'\\\\nGLOBAL SUMMARY: {global_summary[0][\\\"summary_text\\\"]}')\\n    except: pass\\n    return summaries\\n\\nsummaries = chunk_summarize(LONG_DOC)\\nfor s in summaries:\\n    print(s)\\n    print()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Chunk-based summarization handles documents longer than model context windows.**\\n\",\"- **Chapter-wise summaries preserve document structure.**\\n\",\"- **Global summary synthesizes across chapters.**\\n\",\"- **For production, use map-reduce or refine strategies** with longer-context models.\"]}\n",
